#      → Upload LCME doc once, reuse cached version in all Phase 1 & 2 calls
#   6. ADDED retry logic with exponential backoff
#
# Expected speedup: 8 hours → ~30-45 minutes
# Expected cost reduction: ~80%
# =============================================================================

